structure.unit: OFFENSES AGAINST THE STATE AND PUBLIC JUSTICE

law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491, effective January 2, 1978. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 273. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1291, 1301, 1302.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Limit of penalty for contempt -- Removal of officer exceeding limit.
